st.html | work=12 Gauge Comics | title=Paolo Parente's Dust | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081019093910/http://www.12gaugecomics.com/dust.html | archivedate=2008-10-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dustgame.com | title=Paolo Parente\u2019s Dust: The Army Weekly}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/news/newsitem.cgi?id=9533 | title=''Dust'' Debuts From mink and Parente This Summer at Image | date=February 1, 2007 | work=Comic Book Resources}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/news/newsitem.cgi?id=11715 | title=Preview: ''Dust'' #2 | date=August 28, 2007 | work=Comic Book Resources}}</ref>\n* ''Dusty Star''\n* ''[[DV8]]''\n* ''[[Dynamo 5]]'' (2007\u20132009)\n\n===E===\n* ''[[East of West]]'' (2013 \u2013 ongoing)\n* ''[[Eclipse (comic's)|Eclipse]]'' (2017\u2013)\n* ''[[Elephantmen]]'' (2006\u20132018)\n* ''Elsewhere'' (2017\u2013)\n* ''Empty Zone'' (2015-)\n* ''[[Enormous (comic)|Enormous]]'' (former publisher; 2012\u20132015 and ''Kaiju is Giant Animal''/''Creatures in Series'')\n* ''Eternal Empire'' (2017\u2013)\n* ''The Expatriate'' (2005\u20132006)\n* ''[[Extreme Sacrifice]]'' (1995)\n* ''Extremity'' (2017\u2013)\n\n===F===\n* ''[[Faction Paradox]]''\n* ''[[The Fade Out]]'' (2014\u20132016)\n*''Fairlady'' (2019\u2013)\n* ''[[Fall Out Toy Works]]'' (2009\u20132010)<ref>{{cite web | first=Cindy | last=Clark | url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2009-08-31-wentz-comic-book_N.htm | title=Fall Out Dad Pete Wentz Has a 'Fall Out' Comic-Book Series | work=[[USA Today]] | date=August 31, 2009 | accessdate=2009-09-01}}</ref>\n*''Farmhand'', by [[Taylor Wells]] and [[Rob Guillory]] (2018\u2013)\n* ''[[Fatale (Image Comics)|Fatale]]''\n* ''[[Fear Agent]]'' (2005\u20132010)\n* ''[[Fearless (comics)|Fearless]]''\n* ''Feather''\n* ''[[Fell (comics)|Fell]]'' (2005\u20132008)\n* ''[[Ferro City]]'' (2005)\n* ''[[Fire From Heaven (comics)|Fire From Heaven]]''\n* ''[[Firebreather]]''\